snippet.title: Limit Theory Gameplay Demo 5
snippet.description:
Demonstrating asteroid bases, carrier ships, and landing on stuff in Limit Theory. Learn more at http://LTheory.com. Support the dream at http://kickstarter.LTheory.com ! We've only got 30 hours to go, so now's your chance if you want to support LT!

Sorry about the random microphone sounds..my mic really decided to act up today.
